name: [ aequalis voluptas ]
description:
~ equal pleasure ~
.
.
"have you escaped your dream?
or just avoiding reality?
your guilty conscience was playing tricks on me,
was pointing finger on me,
I am to blame one more time...

that sweet reminiscence,
has been kept in your deepest ravine.
as we were connected,
you will return to me eventually,
to renew the evergreen melody....

as there was no consequences"
--180715
.
.
Graphite pencils on paper, with digital touch.
